item.title: A New Journey
item.description:
A New Journey

So, here we go. Another tiny footprint on the vast landscape of cyberspace. Does anyone say cyberspace any more? The other day our twelve year old daughter said "you're so old - you were born in the 1900s." Yes, just a tad older than the original Star Wars is getting up there I suppose. How clever is this Grid? A trail of micro-experiments in e-journaling might shed some light.Â
